timeline.bodyText:
The map contains lists with one element, so ordering is applying to that list and therefore not working.
Perhaps you can order after generating the list of CaseMilestoneInstance.
milestones.sort(Comparator.comparing(CaseMilestoneInstance::getAchievedAt));

